      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>A Love To Throw</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Not far from reason</l>
          <l>And not so far from home</l>
          <l>I picked a flower I smelled it for so long</l>
          <l>I dont want to force things in me</l>
          <l>Although I wish</l>
          <l>That I will find a place for love </l>
          <l>Im not wise enough</l>
          <l>To open up and let you through</l>
          <l>Were not far from parting</l>
          <l>Not far from loving too</l>
          <l>Its all in the mist right now</l>
          <l>Hard to tell whats in our path</l>
          <l>Its hard to settle for something less </l>
          <l>This evening will lead us</l>
          <l>To a point of no return</l>
          <l>A break to hold by</l>
          <l>A love to throw</l>
          <l>A break to hold by</l>
          <l>A love to throw</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
